sources.description:
PizzaFLIX Marathon Edition! Complete 15-chapter Cliffhanger!
Starring: Ralph Byrd, Lynne Roberts, Charles Middleton, David Sharpe
Writer: Chester Gould (comic strip by)
Directors:  John English & William Witney
Ralph Byrd stars as the granite-jawed detective, DICK TRACY, who battles spies and saboteurs in his efforts to take down a notorious crime family led by the vicious Pa Stark.
